---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">What we offer</span>
    <h1>Whole-person care<br>for your whole life.</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">Every service at Behold Your Wonder is designed around one idea — that your mind, body, and support system are not separate things.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-grid">
      <div class="intro-sticky fade-up">
        <h2>Care that connects the dots</h2>
        <p>You don't have to navigate your care alone. Every service at BYW is coordinated — your Mental Health Coordinator ensures nothing falls through the cracks from your very first day with us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-list">
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <span class="service-tag tag-included">Included with all plans</span>
          <h3 class="service-title">Mental Health Coordination</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">Every client is assigned a Mental Health Coordinator on intake. Your coordinator manages your scheduling, ensures you are connected to the right clinician or specialist, and serves as your administrative point of contact throughout your time with us.</p>
          <p class="service-includes">What's included</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Dedicated coordinator from day one</li>
            <li>Scheduling and calendar management</li>
            <li>Referral coordination with specialist network</li>
            <li>Follow-up and continuity support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <span class="service-tag tag-subscription">Subscription</span>
          <h3 class="service-title">Async Clinical Support</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">Direct messaging access to your clinical team between sessions. Ask a question, share what came up this week, or flag something that cannot wait. Responses are delivered by your licensed clinician within an agreed window. This is not a bot — it is your therapist, accessible in a format that fits your life.</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Secure direct messaging to your clinician</li>
            <li>Agreed response window (typically 24 hours)</li>
            <li>Available as standalone or included in care plans</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <span class="service-tag tag-session">Per session or monthly plan</span>
          <h3 class="service-title">1:1 Therapy</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">Individual therapy sessions with a licensed clinician experienced in women's hormonal mental health. Sessions are conducted via secure telehealth and are available weekly or bi-weekly. Our therapists draw on evidence-based modalities adapted to the specific context of hormonal and reproductive mental health.</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Licensed therapists with hormonal health specialization</li>
            <li>Weekly or bi-weekly sessions via secure telehealth</li>
            <li>CBT, Psychodynamic, Humanistic, somatic approaches, and proprietary CMBT</li>
            <li>PMDD, perinatal, perimenopause, fertility grief</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <span class="service-tag tag-membership">Monthly membership</span>
          <h3 class="service-title">Group Workshops</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">Clinician-facilitated group sessions organized around shared experience — perimenopause, postpartum adjustment, fertility journeys, hormonal mood disorders, and more. Groups are intentionally small, therapeutically structured, and held in a consistent cohort so that real trust and depth are possible.</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Small cohort groups (max 8 members)</li>
            <li>Condition-specific groupings</li>
            <li>Clinician-facilitated, therapeutically grounded</li>
            <li>Consistent membership for depth and continuity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card fade-up">
          <span class="service-tag tag-session">Per event</span>
          <h3 class="service-title">Workshops & Conferences</h3>
          <p class="service-desc">Educational events developed and delivered by our clinical team, often in partnership with our specialist network. Topics span the intersection of hormonal health and mental wellbeing. Rigorous content. Practical application. No wellness fluff.</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>Understanding the luteal phase and mood</li>
            <li>Navigating the emotional complexity of infertility</li>
            <li>What perimenopause actually does to the brain</li>
            <li>CMBT certification training for clinicians</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="network">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="network-head fade-up">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Specialist partner network</span>
      <h2>Your specialist knows who you are<br>before you walk in.</h2>
      <p>When you need a specialist, we don't hand you a list and wish you well. Our vetted partner network works in coordination with your clinical team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="specialist-grid fade-up">
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">OBGYNs</p><p class="specialist-role">Obstetrics & Gynecology</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Reproductive Endocrinologists</p><p class="specialist-role">Fertility & hormonal medicine</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">PMHNPs</p><p class="specialist-role">Psychiatric medication support</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Women's Health NPs</p><p class="specialist-role">Hormonal & reproductive health</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Endocrinologists</p><p class="specialist-role">Thyroid & hormonal conditions</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Birth & Postpartum Doulas</p><p class="specialist-role">Labor & postpartum support</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Lactation Consultants</p><p class="specialist-role">IBCLCs — breastfeeding support</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Fertility Coaches</p><p class="specialist-role">IVF, loss & fertility navigation</p></div></div>
      <div class="specialist-pill"><div class="specialist-dot"></div><div><p class="specialist-name">Acupuncturists</p><p class="specialist-role">Integrative hormonal support</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services-cta">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light">Ready to begin</span>
    <h2>Your first step is a conversation.</h2>
    <p>Your 25-minute consult with your Mental Health Coordinator. No pressure, no commitment.</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a href="https://beholdyourwonder.clientsecure.me" class="btn-primary">Book a 25-minute consultation</a>
      <a href="/cmbt" class="btn-outline-light">Learn about CMBT</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
.page-hero{background:var(--ink);padding:clamp(64px,10vw,110px) 0;text-align:center}
.page-hero h1{color:#fff;margin-bottom:18px}
.page-hero-sub{font-size:clamp(14px,1.8vw,16px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);line-height:1.75;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto}

.services-intro{background:var(--cream);padding:var(--pad) 0}
.intro-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;gap:clamp(32px,5vw,64px);align-items:start}
.intro-sticky{position:sticky;top:108px}
.intro-sticky h2{color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:16px}
.intro-sticky p{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.85}

.service-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:clamp(16px,2vw,24px)}
.service-card{background:#fff;border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:clamp(24px,3vw,36px);transition:border-color 0.2s}
.service-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold)}
.service-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);margin-bottom:14px}
.tag-included{background:rgba(245,184,0,0.15);color:var(--gold-dk)}
.tag-subscription{background:rgba(30,30,30,0.06);color:var(--ink-soft)}
.tag-session{background:rgba(125,217,138,0.15);color:#2E7D5E}
.tag-membership{background:rgba(168,223,254,0.2);color:#1A6A9A}
.service-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px);color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:300}
.service-desc{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,14px);color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px}
.service-includes{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:8px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em}
.service-features{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.service-features li{font-size:clamp(12px,1.3vw,13px);color:var(--ink-soft);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;line-height:1.6}
.service-features li::before{content:'';width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:7px}

.network{background:var(--ink);padding:var(--pad) 0}
.network-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:clamp(36px,5vw,52px)}
.network-head h2{color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px}
.network-head p{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-top:12px;max-width:520px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.specialist-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:clamp(10px,1.5vw,14px)}
.specialist-pill{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:var(--radius-md);padding:18px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;transition:background 0.2s}
.specialist-pill:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}
.specialist-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0}
.specialist-name{font-size:clamp(12px,1.4vw,14px);font-weight:500;color:#fff}
.specialist-role{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:2px}

.services-cta{background:var(--gold);padding:var(--pad) 0;text-align:center}
.services-cta h2{color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:14px}
.services-cta p{font-size:clamp(13px,1.5vw,15px);color:rgba(30,30,30,0.65);line-height:1.75;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 32px}
.btn-outline-light{border:1.5px solid rgba(30,30,30,0.4);color:var(--ink);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;padding:13px 30px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);display:inline-block;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.btn-outline-light:hover{border-color:var(--ink)}

@media(max-width:900px){.intro-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.intro-sticky{position:static}.specialist-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:600px){.specialist-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>

<script>
const observer = new IntersectionObserver(e => {
  e.forEach(t => { if(t.isIntersecting){ t.target.classList.add('visible'); observer.unobserve(t.target); }});
}, {threshold:0.1, rootMargin:'0px 0px -40px 0px'});
document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
